725996f-b.title: Queens: 193rd Street - Jamaica Avenue
725996f-b.text:
193rd Street, east side, between Jamaica Ave. (left), Woodhull
Ave.,(and Holliswood Ave. (right), showing in a set of two views
the Richard A. Homeyer house; occupying lot 20 in block 1772.
April 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
